            <div type="translation">
                <p>And you, (O) Virgin, in death [..]
                   redemption of sin [...]
                   [is] the miracle, and full of every (kind of) fright
                   But (it/he/she) will not possess/restaint the [...]
                   [she who] bears the Lord the Logos (<bibl><ptr target="#Ševčenko2012"/>, <citedRange> 81</citedRange></bibl></p> 
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Poor condition. Partially preserved. A cross with arrays in the angles marks the end of the text. Based on the other examples (metrical inscriptions), a similar cross could have occurred at the beginning of the text.</p>
            </div>
